{"tid":2281983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無懼疫症 4成英國青年聖誕準備出遊","createTime":"2020-11-11T13:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T12:17:57.000Z","uid":199670,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0c6e59b20815af1db37ce888c0badd3e571cc068","tid":2281983,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:34:17.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎於歐洲並無消退跡象，英國剛宣佈新一輪維持4星期嘅禁足令，不過民眾已經極為不滿，最新民調就顯示 <span class=\"red\">4成年輕人表示聖誕期間一定會外遊。</span><br />\n<br />\n首相Boris Johnson再次公佈新一輪4星期禁足令，表示明白民眾已經厭倦，不過希望大家能夠遵守措拖，聖誕前可以回復正常。不過民眾一於少理，<span class=\"red\">18歲至24歲英國受訪民眾就話就算聖誕時有無禁足令都好亦唔會理會，一定會外出玩樂食飯，更會外遊至英國其他地方旅遊。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%84%A1%E6%87%BC%E7%96%AB%E7%97%87%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E7%A6%81%E8%B6%B3-4-%E6%88%90%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E8%81%96%E8%AA%95%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E5%87%BA%E9%81%8A-074306985.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2587%25BC%25E7%2596%25AB%25E7%2597%2587%25E6%258B%2592%25E7%25B5%2595%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%25B6%25B3-4-%25E6%2588%2590%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25BC%2595%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2581%2596%25E8%25AA%2595%25E6%25BA%2596%25E5%2582%2599%25E5%2587%25BA%25E9%2581%258A-074306985.html&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVEWzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=ff6ffaf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%84%A1%E6%87%BC%E7%96%AB%E7%97%87%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E7%A6%81%E8%B6%B3-4-%E6%88%90%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E8%81%96%E8%AA%95%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E5%87%BA%E9%81%8A-074306985.html</a>"},{"pid":"3c4658789c0cf192eea0fe10ad50be5fa3b87e9d","tid":2281983,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:34:57.000Z","msg":"白皮豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔見棺材唔流眼淚 中左跳得1cm <img src=\"/a